snippet.title: Shipping Out Trailer
snippet.description: Being the new kid in town is not an easy life. Especially when you know it won’t be the last time. This is not your family’s first move, you have never been able to plant roots . It's your first day at a new school, and something strange is going on around town. You only have a year before you move again, so you better make the most of it. Explore the town, make friends, and live life to its fullest in Shipping Out.
